00:06:11.739 --> 00:06:15.940
that we trust to actually decide these things there. So that's what we kind of a bottom

00:06:15.940 --> 00:06:19.500
up approach to security, where we start with nothing and we just include approved packages

00:06:19.500 --> 00:06:26.420
we want to use. Most talks of security risks always usually jump straight to vulnerabilities,

