which are, of course, more conventional security risks that you want to worry about. And when

00:06:32.820 --> 00:06:37.299
you're worried about, the nice thing about public package repositories is that public

00:06:37.299 --> 00:06:42.140
packages that have been published in one of these repositories really is a known quantity.

